# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PriceModeling — commit CODE + DOCS + FIXTURES only. Everything a run produces
# (data, caches, fitted models, reports, figures, the weather cube, the lake) is
# regenerated from the pipeline and is NOT versioned. See docs/INSTALL.md.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# --- secrets ---------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
*.cdsapirc

# --- raw data, databases, the lake, the weather cube (all rebuildable) ------
/data/
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.duckdb
*.nc
*.parquet

# --- per-model generated artifacts (calibrations, projections, caches) ------
**/output/
**/models/
**/.cache/
**/era5_cache/

# --- generated reports & figures (committed docs are *.md, kept) ------------
**/reports/*.json
**/reports/*.html
**/reports/*.csv
**/reports/*.png
**/reports/*.npz
**/reports/figures/

# --- legacy per-model workbooks (superseded by the root scenarios.xlsx, ADR-5)
#     and generated workbook templates. Keep only scenarios.xlsx.
assumptions*.xlsx
**/assumptions*.xlsx
*_template.xlsx
**/*_template.xlsx

# --- generated API docs (built on demand via scripts/build_docs.py) ---------
/docs/api/

# --- golden harness: keep baseline.json, ignore backups ---------------------
golden/*.bak

# --- logs -------------------------------------------------------------------
*.log

# --- Python -----------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.venv/
venv/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.ipynb_checkpoints/
